summary: Judge was a minor supporting character in Miles Morales Ultimate Comics storyline, one that I was disappointed never really went...
body:
Judge was a minor supporting character in Miles Morales Ultimate Comics storyline, one that I was disappointed never really went anywhere before Bendis unceremoniously put him on a bus. He almost functioned as a audience surrogate to some degree with how much he snarked at Miles and Ganke Lee’s antics.

A lot of the SM fandom expended their energy on comparing Michelle Jones to Mary Jane Watson (because Mary Jane’s nickname was basically superimposed on Jones), but after I saw this art piece,  I haven’t been able to un-see the parallels. Michelle Jones isn’t Mary Jane, she basically is a repurposing of Judge from Ultimate Comics Spider-Man, right down to the exasperation aimed toward Miles!Peter and Ned!Ganke.
